### Add review
POST http://localhost:8080/api/review
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Roles: USER

{
  "productId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Great product!"
}

### Get product reviews
GET http://localhost:8080/api/review/product/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111?page=0

### Admin - Approve review
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/review/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111/approve
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Roles: ADMIN

{
  "isApproved": true
}
